972
01:09:10,215 --> 01:09:12,924
well I’ll only be… half a world away.

973
01:09:17,327 --> 01:09:19,037
Go find happiness, mom.

974
01:09:19,780 --> 01:09:20,753
I love you.

975
01:09:24,109 --> 01:09:25,232
I love you, too.

976
01:10:51,848 --> 01:10:53,583
